Privacy Policy for Billuu Advert Bot.

Effective Date: October 6, 2024

1. Introduction
This Privacy Policy explains how Billuu Advert ("we," "our," or "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our Telegram bot. By using our bot, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information from users:

User Data: Telegram username, chat ID, and interaction history.

Trading Preferences: Information related to your market preferences, such as selected financial instruments or signals.

Communication Data: Messages and responses sent to the bot for processing your requests.


We do not collect personal identifiable information (such as your name or email) unless explicitly shared.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data to:

Provide you with real-time trading signals, market updates, and alerts.

Improve the functionality and performance of the bot.

Customize user experiences based on preferences.

Communicate important updates regarding the bot.


4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not share, sell, or rent your data to third parties. However, we may disclose your information:

If required by law or legal process.

To protect the rights, property, and safety of the bot or other users.


5. Data Security

We take reasonable steps to protect the information we collect from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

6. Data Retention

We will retain your data for as long as necessary to provide our services or as required by law. You can request the deletion of your data by contacting us directly.

7. User Rights

You have the following rights regarding your data:

Access your data: Request a copy of the data we have on you.

Correct your data: Update or correct any inaccuracies in your information.

Delete your data: Request the deletion of your data from our system.


To exercise any of these rights, please contact us via bsafi968@gmail.com

8. Third-Party Services

Our bot may contain links to external services or use third-party APIs (such as trading platforms). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party services. We encourage you to read their privacy policies before interacting with them.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the bot, and your continued use of the bot after such changes will constitute your acknowledgment of the changes.

10. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or the handling of your information, please contact us at bsafi968@gmail.com
